Recommends: pamac-manager | synaptic | gnome-software
Description: Apple menu plugin for XFCE4 panel
 A panel plugin for XFCE4 that mimics the macOS Apple menu, providing
 a familiar and intuitive system menu experience for XFCE desktop users.
 .
 Features:
  - Apple-style dropdown menu with Apple logo
  - System information display
  - Quick access to system preferences
  - Package management integration
  - System actions (sleep, restart, shutdown, lock, logout)
  - Configurable options and transparency
